data.description: Impeccably maintained and ready-to-move-in townhome situated on Ankeny's Northwest side. This charming two-story townhouse boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, and a 2-car attached garage. The main floor features an inviting open layout with custom built-ins, a convenient 1/2 bath, a galley-style kitchen, and an open dining area. Upstairs, discover three spacious bedrooms, a laundry room, a full bath, and a master suite equipped with dual sinks and a walk-in closet. This home is a must-see, showcasing numerous upgrades and the added advantage of backing up to the high trestle trail.  All information obtained from seller and public records.
